## tool-tool-preview-length: tool_preview_length tool definition

### tool_preview_length(action: str, value: int = None) → str
Control how many characters of tool output are shown in the chat UI.
The full result is always sent to the LLM regardless of this setting.
- action="get" — show the current limit.
- action="set" — change the limit (value=0 means unlimited, default=500).
Always allowed — no gate required.
